      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im looking at my insulin for tonight. i barely ate anything for dinner, like just a few bites of salad. is it okay if i just skip my basal dose tonight so my blood sugar doesnt drop too low? feels like i dont really need it if i didn't eat much.",
