      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the thing is, if i take the full dose on an empty stomach, isn't that *more* likely to make me crash? like, logically, if there's no food to balance the insulin, my sugar will just plummet. if i just take half the dose instead, wouldn't that be a safer middle ground for tonight? most people say you can adjust based on what you eat.",
